hJax_Math-italic" class="mi">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>需要是一个满秩方阵。</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 易证，当上述方程<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; line-height: normal; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px" class="MathJax"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 4.544em" class="math"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 3.624em; height: 0px; font-size: 17px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; clip: rect(1.957em 1000.012em 2.992em -0.457em); top: -2.814em; left: 0.003em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="mrow"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">A</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">X</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.29em; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main" class="mo">=</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.29em; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="texatom"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="mrow"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main-bold" class="mi">b</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>是相容方程（即有解），此时<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; line-height: normal; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px" class="MathJax"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 1.038em" class="math"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 0.808em; height: 0px; font-size: 17px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; clip: rect(1.612em 1000.012em 2.647em -0.457em); top: -2.469em; left: 0.003em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="mrow"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>要满足的条件是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; line-height: normal; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px" class="MathJax"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 5.464em" class="math"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 4.372em; height: 0px; font-size: 17px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; clip: rect(1.9em 1000.012em 2.935em -0.457em); top: -2.756em; left: 0.003em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="mrow"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">A</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">B</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">A</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.29em; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main" class="mo">=</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.29em; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>。按照求解线性方程组的思路，矩阵的逆、广义逆、伪逆、矩阵的秩出现得就自然而然了。求解过程中需要应用到矩阵的满秩分解，范数等知识。</p><h2 style="margin: 15px auto 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑" align="left">2. 矩阵计算的根本是什么</h2><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当然，计算过程中，不是求解一个线性方程组的解就够了的。就拿优化问题来说，解决问题的基本思路中要使用求导（求梯度）。如果我们仅仅是将问题采用矩阵表示，的确是简洁了，但不会求解（求导）又有什么用呢？而从就矩阵仅仅问题的一种表示方法而言，矩阵的运算<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #ff0000">不应该是一种全新的运算法则，而应和数的计算相契合</span>。</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 先考虑一个最简单的，如下所示</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?f%28x_1%2Cx_2%2C...%2Cx_n%29%3Da_1x_1&amp;plus;a_2x_2&amp;plus;..&amp;plus;a_nx_n" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 矩阵（向量）表示是</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?f%28X%29%3Da%5ETX" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 导数表示为</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5Cfrac%7B%5Cpartial%20f%28X%29%7D%7B%5Cpartial%20X%7D" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 第一个问题是，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #4f81bd">求导到底求的是什么？</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px">一直以来，我们只会对一个变量求导，导数是切线的斜率；即使是多变量，也是一个一个求偏导。当然，导数的另一个理解是一阶逼近，即</span></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?f%28X&amp;plus;%5CDelta%20X%29%3Df%28X%29&amp;plus;%5Cfrac%7B%5Cpartial%20f%28X%29%7D%7B%5Cpartial%20X%7D%5CDelta%20X" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp; 从这一点来说，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #ff0000">数量函数对向量（矩阵）求导实际上是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px">（矩阵导数有其严格定义，此处不做说明）</span></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5Cfrac%7B%5Cpartial%20f%28X%29%7D%7B%5Cpartial%20X%7D%20%3D%20%5B%5Cfrac%7B%5Cpartial%20f%28X%29%7D%7B%5Cpartial%20x_1%7D%2C%5Cfrac%7B%5Cpartial%20f%28X%29%7D%7B%5Cpartial%20x_2%7D%2C...%5Cfrac%7B%5Cpartial%20f%28X%29%7D%7B%5Cpartial%20x_m%7D%5D%5ET" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 所以这个最简单例子的求导结果是<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?a" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />，这个例子说明了有关矩阵求导的两个特点：定义不是瞎定义的，是和数值函数导数相符合的；求解实际上是分别对矩阵（向量）中的元素分别求偏导。当然，这个例子引出了一个新的问题&mdash;&mdash;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #ff0000">既然最后我们还要分别求偏导，那么为何我们还要写成矩阵形式？</span></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #ff0000">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px">这个问题的解答有两点：一是针对数量函数对矩阵的导数而言，也有基本的运算公式可以使用，而且有一些基本的导数是显而易见的；其二是有时候我们可以直接利用定义以及矩阵的性质求解，譬如前段时间同学问的问题</span></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?Df%28x%29%3D%5Cfrac%7B%5Cpartial%20%5Cmathbf%7Btr%7D%28AX%5E%7B-1%7DB%29%7D%7B%5Cpartial%20X%7D" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 可以采用如下方式求解</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5C%5C%20f%28X&amp;plus;%5CDelta%20X%29%3D%5Cmathbf%7Btr%7D%28A%28X&amp;plus;%5CDelta%20X%29%5E%7B-1%7DB%29%20%5C%5C%20%3D%5Cmathbf%7Btr%7D%28A%28X%5E%7B-1%7D-X%5E%7B-1%7D%5CDelta%20XX%5E%7B-1%7D%29B%29%20%5C%5C%20%3Df%28X%29-%5Cmathbf%7Btr%7D%28AX%5E%7B-1%7D%5CDelta%20X%20X%5E%7B-1%7DB%29%20%5C%5C%20%3Df%28X%29-%5Cmathbf%7Btr%7D%28X%5E%7B-1%7DBAX%5E%7B-1%7D%5CDelta%20X%29%20%5C%5C%20%5C%5C%20Df%28X%29%3D-%28X%5E%7B-1%7DBAX%5E%7B-1%7D%29%5ET" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px">那么，回到本节的标题，矩阵计算的根本是什么？<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666">矩阵提供了一种更简洁的描述问题的方式，采用矩阵这一方法表示问题进行计算时，对于矩阵有一套相应的运算规则，这就是矩阵计算。而采用矩阵计算出来的结果，必须是与不利用矩阵计算得出的结果相同的，这是矩阵计算推导过程中要遵循的准则。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px">在这一思路下，包括矩阵求导，积分，微分方程在内的运算就不难理解了。再扩展开一点，包括矩阵序列、级数和函数的计算也遵循这一思路。</span></p><h2 style="margin: 15px auto 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑">3. 空间&mdash;&mdash;让矩阵不仅仅是矩阵</h2><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 矩阵存在的意义难道仅仅只在于给出公式更有利的表示和简单的计算方法？当然不是，要不然矩阵课本也不会花那么大的力气从线性空间讨论起了。当我们回顾本文的第一小节，方程组的解是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; line-height: normal; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px" class="MathJax"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 4.544em" class="math"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 3.624em; height: 0px; font-size: 17px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; clip: rect(1.957em 1000.012em 2.992em -0.514em); top: -2.814em; left: 0.003em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="mrow"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">X</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.29em; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main" class="mo">=</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.29em; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">B</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="texatom"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="mrow"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main-bold" class="mi">b</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>。解是由矩阵、向量表示的，这给予我们一种新的思路&mdash;&mdash;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333">矩阵不仅简洁的表示了公式，矩阵还能够表示解</span></strong>。</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有一点是很好理解的，那就是如果<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?X%5Cin%20R%5En" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />，那么</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?X%3D%28x_1%2Cx_2%2C...%2Cx_n%29" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 其中<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?x_1%2Cx_2%2C...%2Cx_n%5Cin%20R" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />，我们似乎已经很习惯了这种表示，但是是否思考过为何能这样表示呢？这一表示至少意味着<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?R%5En" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />具有以下性质，对于<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?X%2CY%5Cin%20R%5En" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5C%5C%20X&amp;plus;Y%3DY&amp;plus;X%5C%5C%20%28k&amp;plus;l%29X%3DkX&amp;plus;lX%5C%5C%20k%28X&amp;plus;Y%29%3DkX&amp;plus;kY%5C%5C%20..." border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 实际上<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?R%5En" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />是一线性空间，正是因为<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?R%5En" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />是线性空间，我们才能够利用一组基表示这一空间中的元素。当然，基显然不是唯一的。拿<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?R%5E2" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />空间来说，<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5C%7B%280%2C1%29%2C%281%2C0%29%5C%7D" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />是一组基；<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5C%7B%280%2C1%29%2C%281%2C1%29%5C%7D" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />也是一组基。空间中的任意一向量可以表示为</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5Cbeta%20%3D%20%5Csum%7Bk_i%5Calpha_i%7D" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 由此引出两个问题：不同基之间对应<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?k_i" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />的关系是什么；哪组基更好。第一个问题的结论很简单，如果</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5B%5Calpha_1%2C...%2C%5Calpha_n%5D%3DP%5B%5Cbeta_1%2C...%2C%5Cbeta_n%5D" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 那么坐标之间的关系为<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; line-height: normal; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px" class="MathJax"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 6.211em" class="math"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 4.947em; height: 0px; font-size: 17px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; clip: rect(1.9em 1000.012em 3.222em -0.457em); top: -2.756em; left: 0.003em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="mrow"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="msubsup"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 1.44em; height: 0px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; clip: rect(1.612em 1000.012em 2.647em -0.457em); top: -2.469em; left: 0.003em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">K</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; top: -1.894em; left: 0.865em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">&alpha;</span></span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.29em; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main" class="mo">=</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.29em; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">P</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="msubsup"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 1.383em; height: 0px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; clip: rect(1.612em 1000.012em 2.647em -0.457em); top: -2.469em; left: 0.003em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">K</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; top: -1.894em; left: 0.865em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">&beta;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，不同基下的坐标之间的关系，我们可以理解为一种线性变换，即<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; line-height: normal; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px" class="MathJax"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 6.441em" class="math"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 5.119em; height: 0px; font-size: 17px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; clip: rect(1.842em 1000.012em 3.165em -0.457em); top: -2.756em; left: 0.003em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="mrow"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">f</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main" class="mo">(</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">X</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main" class="mo">)</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.29em; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main" class="mo">=</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.29em; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">A</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">X</span></span></span></span></span></span>。第二个问题，则必须提出一个合适的评判标准了。引入线性变换后，这个问题可以转换为另一个问题&mdash;&mdash;具体来说，实际上线性变换的矩阵<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; line-height: normal; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px" class="MathJax"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 1.038em" class="math"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 0.808em; height: 0px; font-size: 17px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; clip: rect(1.612em 1000.012em 2.647em -0.457em); top: -2.469em; left: 0.003em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="mrow"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">P</span></span></span></span></span></span>针对不同的基具有不同的表达形式，也就是说我们只要关心矩阵<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; line-height: normal; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px" class="MathJax"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 1.038em" class="math"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 0.808em; height: 0px; font-size: 17px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; clip: rect(1.612em 1000.012em 2.647em -0.457em); top: -2.469em; left: 0.003em"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px" class="mrow"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic" class="mi">P</span></span></span></span></span></span>就足够了。关于线性变换，<a style="margin: 0px; padding: 1px 3px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; color: green" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matrix_(mathematics)">wiki</a>上有如下的图示</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px"><a style="margin: 0px; padding: 1px 3px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; color: green" href="http://images.cnitblog.com/blog/663760/201412/212039281878201.png"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline; background-image: none" src="http://images.cnitblog.com/blog/663760/201412/212039303748800.png" border="0" alt="image" title="image" width="591" height="174" /></a></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 上图表示了在<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?R%5E2" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />下不同变换矩阵时的变化关系，其中蓝色是原始空间，绿色是映射后的图示。那么到这里可以解释&ldquo;哪组基更好&rdquo;，这取决于你更希望你的空间满足什么样的几何需求。</p><h2 style="margin: 15px auto 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑">4. 特征向量的特征</h2><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 映射（这里指线性变换）往往使得取值发生变化，然而我们总是希望在变化寻求一个不变的量，称之为特征。如果某一向量在经过线性变化后保持其方向的不变性，即<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?AX%3D%5Clambda%20X" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />那么就称<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?X" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />为特征向量，<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5Clambda" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />为相应的特征值。脱离实际例子来谈&ldquo;特征&rdquo;很不&ldquo;特征&rdquo;，关于这一部分内容可以参考<a style="margin: 0px; padding: 1px 3px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; color: green" href="http://www.cnblogs.com/LeftNotEasy/archive/2011/01/19/svd-and-applications.html">机器学习中的数学(5)-强大的矩阵奇异值分解(SVD)及其应用</a>，解释很详细并有距离。一点小的瑕疵是没有阐明SVD和特征值之间的关系，举例中有一点小错误。本节接下来的内容将致力于阐明矩阵对角化的相关联系。</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 求解特征值就是求解<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%28A-%5Clambda%20I%29X%3D0" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />，如果<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?A" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />是一个对角阵，那么显然有特征值为<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?a_%7B11%7D%2Ca_%7B22%7D%2C...%2Ca_%7Bnn%7D" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />。有注意的是特征值和线性变换是密不可分的，完了，写不下去了&hellip;&hellip;我自己也说不明白了&hellip;&hellip;</p><hr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" /><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">鉴于原先思路已经写不下去了，那就先简单讲讲各个对角化之间的关系吧。</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 对于同一线性变换而言，不同基下的矩阵表示满足（相似关系）</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="center"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?B%3DP%5E%7B-1%7DAP" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." /></p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 前文还是说明了一点，那就是对角矩阵对于一个线性变换来说是极其的方便的，所以我们希望矩阵能够<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #ff0000">相似于一个对角阵</span>。但是很不幸的是，不是所有的矩阵都能相似于对角阵，于是提出了一个Jordan标准型的东西。（还没怎么遇到过涉及Jordan标准型的问题）</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 而更多情况是，我们不仅仅想要相似对角阵<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?A%3DP%5E%7B-1%7Ddiag%28a_1%2Ca_2%2C...%2Ca_n%29%20P" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />，还对<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?P" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />有要求，毕竟其列向量就是特征向量。我们希望一组基是正交的，归一化的。也就是说<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?P%5EHP%3DI" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />，这就是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #ff0000">酉对角化</span>的概念。酉对角化要求更为严苛，需满足<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?A%5EHA%3DAA%5EH" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />。</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">Hermite矩阵是满足这一条件的，那么对于任意一个矩阵，我们可以通过求<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?A%5EHA" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />或是<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?AA%5EH" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />的酉对角化求得<img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px" src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?A" border="0" title="This is the rendered form of the equation. You can not edit this directly. Right click will give you the option to save the image, and in most browsers you can drag the image onto your desktop or another program." />的<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #ff0000">奇异值分解</span>。</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px" align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 也就是说，在相似对角化的基础上进行约束或是妥协，尽可能的发现矩阵的<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #ff0000">特征。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px">所以矩阵的很多内容在讲对角化，目的大抵如此。</span></p><h2 style="margin: 15px auto 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑">5. 总结</h2><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.4结写得有点混乱不堪，矩阵方面的知识还需要进一步的掌握。或许要了解到足够多的实际问题，在解决的过程中体会才会有更深的理解。</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 而学习过程中多问几个为什么，为什么要做这样做以及这样做的好处是什么，对学习将会是大有裨益的。</p><p style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.8800010681152px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 本文如有什么错误或是不足，还请大家指正。而且居然还总结不下去了&hellip;&hellip;</p>
